Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.05,0:24:37.00,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)\3c&H59200E&}將尚未預料到的春分呼喚而來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.51,0:24:41.56,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)\3c&H2C3689&}雙目相和便是微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.78,0:24:44.18,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)\3c&H7181EC&}放學後經常
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.46,0:24:44.35,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)\3c&H2C3689&}在你的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.49,0:24:47.83,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)\3c&H7181EC&}身邊度過
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.94,0:24:53.40,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}晴朗的一天 聽見了呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.42,0:24:57.14,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}描繪起美好的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.17,0:25:00.43,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)\3c&H92B4F7&}純白的可能性 So Want Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.55,0:25:05.13,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}想像日記 隻言片語便是主題
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.35,0:25:09.09,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}雖然已然知曉 卻仍想全部瀏覽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.30,0:25:11.83,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}要確認真實的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.95,0:25:15.76,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}就算背負著沉重的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.97,0:25:19.66,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}也要多陪伴在我的身邊
